                                            <td>单击  <img src="~/Images/Help/image007.png" width=13 height=23>图标打开流程状态，通过此页面可以看到该张PR单的流程情况及当前节点。</td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td> <img src="~/Images/Help/image008.jpg" width=472 height=183></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr style="height:35px">
                                            <td>单击 <img src="~/Images/Help/image009.png" width=17 height=24> 图标打开申请单，此时PR单状态为查看状态。</td>
